E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister, Rude(ish) Tube, featuring sports of the lawnmower, motorbike and bicycle variety.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Junior Bake Off
E4Plus1.uk.description: The bakers take on Bread Day, as they make pizza and recreate their 'roll' models. Who'll steal a pizza the judge's hearts? And whose 'roll' model will see them rise? (S11 Ep3/15) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Iberville: The Nightmare Continues: Gordon's still helping Iberville Cuisine, in New Orleans' French Quarter. Will the staff walk out and implement their plan B? (S9 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Barry Goldberg's Day Off: Inspired by the film Ferris Bueller's Day Off, Barry pretends to be ill so he can avoid school and create an epic day of his own. (S2 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Happy Mom, Happy Life: Dana and Adam are given a doll to parent for a class assignment, but Beverly keeps interfering. (S2 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Day of the Jackanapes: Sideshow Bob swears revenge on Krusty for accidentally erasing the first 10 years of their programme. (S12 Ep13/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: New Kids on the Blecch: After cheating in the Springfield Marathon, Bart is rescued from an angry mob by a record producer and is recruited for a new boy band. (S12 Ep14/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: 3 Southern Girls: When a car accident left her son fighting for his life, Gabi was forced to close her traditional restaurant for over a month. Can Gordon help launch a comeback? (S9 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Kings Blu Jam: With debts mounting, and a 'toxic' dynamic between owner Connie and her manager and daughter Justin, can Gordon turn things around at Kings Blu Jam Caf in Texas? (S9 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Last Barfighter: A secret society of bartenders seek vengeance on Homer and his friends after Moe breaks their most sacred rule. (S32 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Princess Guide: Homer chaperones a Nigerian princess while her father negotiates a uranium deal with Mr Burns. He takes her to Moe's bar, where Moe begins to fall for her. (S26 Ep15/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sky Police: Chief Wiggum uses a military jet pack to fight crime. But when he crashes into the church, Marge and the congregation resort to gambling to pay for the repairs. (S26 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Peeping Mom: Bart lies to cover up his role in a bulldozer crash, so Marge decides to follow him everywhere until he confesses. Ned's cute new dog loves Homer. (S26 Ep18/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Goldbergs Feel Hard: Erica is accepted into a summer arts school, but Murray struggles to express pride in her achievement. Barry becomes the school mascot. (S2 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Kick-Ass Risky Business Party: Lainey, Erica and Barry throw a big party but it spirals out of control. (S3 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Spread Your Wings: With Phil away visiting Alex at college, Claire and the kids seize the opportunity to get the ducklings to leave the house. (S7 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Clean for a Day: Claire tells the family to clean their clutter out of the house but ends up rekindling a whole lot of emotional attachment. (S7 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: 48 Hours: Peralta jumps the gun and makes an arrest without enough evidence, leaving himself only 48 hours to collect the proof he needs before the suspect is released. (S1 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Old School: Peralta is overjoyed when his hero, crime reporter Jimmy Brogan, visits the precinct, but things soon go awry. Jeffords and Boyle prepare Diaz for a day in court. (S1 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Two Mrs Nahasapeemapetilons: Marge agrees to pretend to be Apu's wife when his mother visits to set up his arranged marriage, and Homer moves into the Retirement Castle.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lisa the Skeptic: During a school archaeological dig, Lisa finds the skeleton of an angel on the site where a new shopping mall is to be built. (S9 Ep8/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Desperately Seeking Lisa: Lisa visits Capital City with Patty and Selma, where she's swept up in the city's art scene. But the big city's got an underbelly. (S36 Ep3/18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Shoddy Heat: Grampa finds himself embroiled in a cold case when the police unearth an old coffin with his business card in it - and two bodies. (S36 Ep4/18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Billion Pound Cruise
E4Plus1.uk.description: The cruise ship Symphony of the Seas ports, and with 6680 guests getting off and back on the ship, will it be smooth sailing as they try to keep to their schedule? (Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch Michael McIntyre's The Wheel, Love Is Blind, Strictly Come Dancing, Boiling Point, HELP! My House Is Haunted, and All Creatures Great and Small. (S22 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The TV shows include Big Brother: The Launch, Don't Look Down for SU2C, Antiques Roadshow, Coronation Street, Big Little Journeys and Beat the Chasers Celebrity Special. (S22 Ep6)
